snippet.title: Johnny Depp sues ex-wife Amber Heard for $50 million
snippet.description: A fierce legal battle has broken out between Hollywood stars and divorced couple Johnny Depp and Amber Heard with the former filing a defamation suit against the latter. It was an article written by Amber Heard, regarding domestic violence, which ignited the battle. Depp has accused her of making 'categorically and demonstrably false' allegations. However, Heard's lawyers have produced photographs of her bruised face and scarred arms as proof of abuse.
